title: Chermoula Chicken & Veggie Pearl Couscous with Lemon Yoghurt & Parsley
description: Take your taste buds on a journey with our Middle Eastern-spiced chicken, where aromatic spices transform juicy chicken into a flavourful adventure. Sitting on a bed of roast veggie couscous and dolloped with a citrusy yoghurt, this is a recipe for a hearty bowl you won’t soon forget.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
